{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_02_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私に単独のお仕事が～？\nやったーうれしいっちゃ！",
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……わー！\n今のナシ！　聞かなかったことにして下さーい！",
      "startTime": 9.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さんのその山形弁\n久しぶりに聞いた気がするな",
      "startTime": 15.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁっ、恥ずかしいから言わないで下さい\nいつもは、出ないように気を張ってるんですけど……",
      "startTime": 21.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "ほんとーっに時々、つい油断すると\n出ちゃうんですよね～",
      "startTime": 29.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "無理に直さなくても。鈴村さんだって\n京都弁のままだし、いいんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 34.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんはおしとやかでプラス補正だからいいんです！\n私のは田舎者っぽいから……マイナス補正なんです",
      "startTime": 41.0000001390775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロに入ってアイドルを目指すようになってからは\n一生懸命、矯正したんですよ",
      "startTime": 49.7000001129351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、いまだに驚いたり、興奮したりすると\nつい出ちゃうんですよね……",
      "startTime": 56.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺はいいと思うけどな\nそれだって、奥山さんの個性だろう",
      "startTime": 61.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、天動さんや鈴村さんから\n何か言われたことはある？",
      "startTime": 67,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……ありません\nでも、二人は優しいから",
      "startTime": 71.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "……って、私の方言の話は横に置いておきましょう\nそろそろお仕事の話をして下さいよ～",
      "startTime": 78.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、ごめん。奥山さんに頼みたいのは、今度\n海沿いに開園するウォーターパークのレポーターなんだ",
      "startTime": 87.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "レポーターの仕事のあとに、TRINITYAiLEの\nアピールタイムも用意してもらえたよ",
      "startTime": 93.2160317341487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "私達のライブの宣伝もしていいんですね！\n頑張ります！",
      "startTime": 98.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、放送は地上波だ\n台本はもう出来てる。目を通してくれるか？",
      "startTime": 102.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "はい。ふむふむ……\nうわ～っ、随分大きな施設なんですね",
      "startTime": 110.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 106.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "日本最大級のウォータースライダー！\nイルカと泳げるアトラクション！？",
      "startTime": 118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそうですね！\nすっごいやる気が――ん？　これって……",
      "startTime": 122.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？",
      "startTime": 127.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "……わ",
      "startTime": 128.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "わ？",
      "startTime": 129.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "私が海に入ってはしゃぐって\n書いてるけど、そんな……恥ずかしいっちゃ！！",
      "startTime": 133.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ま、また出たな、その方言\nそれがどうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 140.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "つ、つまり私の水着姿が\n全国ネットで中継されるってことじゃないですか～！？",
      "startTime": 145.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "いや、全国ネットじゃなく\nローカル局で……",
      "startTime": 151.17999997139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、よかった……じゃなくて！\n放送エリアの問題じゃありません！",
      "startTime": 155.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "私、まだ中学生なんですよ！\n水着なんて、恥ずかし過ぎます！！",
      "startTime": 161.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫だ、奥山さん\nそこは俺に考えがある。安心してくれ",
      "startTime": 166.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本当ですか？\nはぁ、よかったです……",
      "startTime": 172.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルには水着風のステージ衣装があるだろ？\nそれを着てレポートしてもらおうと思う",
      "startTime": 178.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "全然大丈夫じゃないっちゃ！！",
      "startTime": 181.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　その衣装でステージに出たことはあるんだろ？\nなら別に恥ずかしくはないんじゃ……",
      "startTime": 188.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　{user}さんは女心を\nぜんっぜん！　分かって！　ないです！",
      "startTime": 196.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "あの衣装を着て……アイドルとして\nステージに上がってパフォーマンスをするのと",
      "startTime": 202.16666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr023.m4a",
      "text": "水着として着て、海に入って\nびしょ濡れになって遊ぶのじゃ――",
      "startTime": 208.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-smr024.m4a",
      "text": "ぜんっぜん！　違い！　ます！",
      "startTime": 210.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_02_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（……どう違うんだ？）\n（女の子の考えることは、時々分からないな……）",
      "startTime": 216.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
